{"tid":2024234,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人睇數碼暴龍除左尾段好感觸之外 一開頭講2個主角都好似見到自己咁","createTime":"2020-05-19T13:08:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T18:11:10.000Z","uid":35562,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4deb793d7350526612362d0901a0f025b3da9313","tid":2024234,"uid":35562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:08:41.000Z","msg":"見到大部份人都係尾段同打鬥喊到仆街 當然我都係<br />\n但見到開頭太一大和唔想大個 只係想靠讀書逃避現實<br />\n唔知自己有咩夢想可言 搵D垃圾PT夠生活就夠<br />\nYR4果年身邊人全部都早大半年搵緊大公司做<br />\n自己就唔知係度做咩 連自己想做邊行都唔知<br />\n我自己U唔係讀專科 重要係因為DSE考得唔夠好先碌左入去<br />\n其實讀左幾年都完全提唔起興趣 雖然成績過得去<br />\n當身邊人問你有咩打算果陣 只會覺得擔心同恐懼<br />\n果一PART雖然未到喊出聲 但真係好真實 我個人覺得寫得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f3e4cc3240a3a9459c81b97bc478e5ac677ee6","tid":2024234,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:22:28.000Z","msg":"小心俾人屌劇透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f2933388c46bd457665741eda98e7b2866b49e","tid":2024234,"uid":35562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11f3e4cc3240a3a9459c81b97bc478e5ac677ee6","tid":2024234,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:22:28.000Z","msg":"小心俾人屌劇透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:27:49.000Z","msg":"其實成個POST都冇咩提過劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31a362c108ad317c2e2044a366d4cee6139db54","tid":2024234,"uid":82889,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T02:13:58.000Z","msg":"認同 <br />\n大和話升學只係想可以多d時間猶豫呢下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41baea87572818a22faf1477e1b0903acaf7f34","tid":2024234,"uid":121855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T03:52:47.000Z","msg":"最希望大家真係睇得明套戲<br />\n套戲並唔係教大家放下 係叫大家拾回<br />\n共勉之"},{"pid":"7df0945683fa76cbf4a8658a7de217d89b601e80","tid":202